### 💥 Failure #11: User pastes a 10MB string into prompt body

**Trigger:** User pastes an extremely long text into the body textarea.

**What happens:**
1. [AdminPromptForm.jsx:84](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/components/admin/AdminPromptForm.jsx#L84) — `e.target.value.slice(0, 4000)` — **client-side limit of 4000 chars**. ✅
